harles, Prince of Wales|publisher=Associated Newspapers|year=1962}}\n* {{Cite book|first=Catherine|last=Mayer|title=Born to Be King: Prince Charles on Planet Windsor|authorlink=Catherine Mayer|publisher=Henry Holt and Co.|year=2015|isbn=978-1627794381|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/borntobekingprin0000maye}}\n* {{Cite book|first=Catherine|last=Mayer|title=Charles: The Heart of a King|authorlink=Catherine Mayer|publisher=Random House|year=2015|isbn=978-0753555934|url=https://archive.org/details/charlesheartofki0000maye}}\n* {{Cite book |last1=Bedell Smith |first1=Sally |title=Prince Charles: The Passions and Paradoxes of an Improbable Life |publisher=Random House Trade Paperbacks |year=2017|isbn=978-0812979800}}\n* {{Cite book |last1=Jobson |first1=Robert |title=Charles at Seventy - Thoughts, Hopes & Dreams: Thoughts, Hopes and Dreams |year=2018 |publisher=John Blake |isbn=978-1786068873}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Sister project links|wikt=no|commons=Category:Charles, Prince of Wales|the Prince of Wales|n=Category:Charles, Prince of Wales|q=Charles, Prince of Wales|s=Author:Charles, Prince of Wales|v=no|voy=no}}\n* [http://www.princeofwales.gov.uk/ Official website of the Prince of Wales]\n* [https://www.royal.uk/the-prince-of-wales The Prince of Wales] at the Royal Family website\n* {{Britannica|107411|Charles, prince of Wales}}\n* [http://www.princes-trust.org.uk/ Official website of 'The Prince's Trust']\n* {{IMDb name| id=0697608|title=The Prince of Wales}}\n* {{C-SPAN|Charles}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-hou|[[House of Windsor]]|14 November|1948}}\n|-\n{{S-other|line}}\n{{S-new|first|reason=[[Heir apparent]]}}\n{{S-ttl|title=[[Succession to the British throne]]|years=1st in line}}\n{{S-fol|after=[[Prince William, Duke of Cambridge|The Duke of Cambridge]]}}\n|-\n{{S-roy|uk}}\n|-\n{{S-vac|rows=2|last=[[Edward VIII|The Prince Edward]]<br /><small>''later became King Edward VIII''</small>}}\n{{S-ttl|title=[[Prince of Wales]]|years=26 Ju